item.title: [Project insanity]How can i create multiple teleports? help please!
item.dc:creator: @James-RevolutionX James-RevolutionX
item.description:
@James-RevolutionX wrote:

The sendOption is the Interface but now to add teleport for Varrock Teleport which is option then when you click on a teleport that you added look at the cmd it should say actionbutton: blbla, for example i’m going to use Rockcrabs, actionbutton: 9190 and the teleaction is 1.

case 9190:
if (c.teleAction == 1) {
//rock crabs
c.getPA().spellTeleport(2676, 3715, 0);
} else if (c.teleAction == 2) {
//barrows
c.getPA().spellTeleport(3565, 3314, 0);
} else if (c.teleAction == 3) {
c.getPA().spellTeleport(2519,4785, 0);
//sea troll queen
} else if (c.teleAction == 4) {
//MageBank
c.getPA().spellTeleport(2539, 4716, 0);
} else if (c.teleAction == 5) {
c.getPA().spellTeleport(2519,4785,0);
}
